---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
import quoteLogo from "../assets/business-govt-nz.png";
import jack from "../assets/jack.png";
import otis from "../assets/otis.jpeg";
import astroLogo from "~/assets/AstroMediaLogo.svg";
---

<div class="flex flex-col sm:mx-32">
  <img src={astroLogo.src} alt="image description" class="my-8 h-16" />
  <ContentSection title="What is Astro Media?" id="intro-section-1">
    <Fragment slot="lead">
      Astro Media was founded in early 2023 because we noticed the lack of
      quality websites in New Zealand, we discovered that many small businesses
      were still using old websites that were slow and often had confusing
      layouts. <br />
      <br />
      This led to Jack Gong, a Software Engineering student and Otis Wales, a Computer
      Science student to come together to make changes in this landscape.

      <br />
      <br />
      Our primary mission is to deliver great websites, which result in <span
        class="text-primary"
        >high conversions.
      </span>
    </Fragment>
  </ContentSection>
  <div class="mt-32 flex flex-col sm:mx-16 xl:mx-32">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-y-4 sm:flex-row">
      <Image
        src={jack}
        class="rounded-2xl bg-default sm:w-1/3"
        alt="business.govt.nz logo"
      />
      <Image
        src={otis}
        class="rounded-2xl bg-default sm:w-1/2"
        alt="business.govt.nz logo"
      />
    </div>
    <p class="italic">
      Founders <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jack-gong/">Jack Gong</a> & <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/otiswales/">Otis Wales</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>

  <figure
    class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-flip p-8 text-center"
  >
    <blockquote class="mx-auto mb-4 max-w-2xl text-flip lg:mb-8">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">
        "No business, whether youâ€™re part-time, self-employed, a start-up or you
        have a large staff, can afford to be without a digital presence."
      </h3>
    </blockquote>
    <a
      href="https://www.business.govt.nz/getting-started/building-a-brand/getting-an-online-presence/"
    >
      <Image
        src={quoteLogo}
        class="w-40 rounded-2xl bg-default p-3 px-4"
        alt="business.govt.nz logo"
      />
    </a>
  </figure>
  <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
    <h2
      class="gradient-text text-center font-extrabold tracking-tight text-6xl"
    >
      How we will help you grow
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-16 grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 border-default bg-offset p-8"
        style="min-height: 300px;"
      >
        <div
          class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-primary p-3 text-primary"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:code-braces-box" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center font-extrabold text-2xl">
          Custom Websites
        </h1>
        <p>
          We develop custom websites which are optimised for speed and ranking,
          we can guarantee fast loading times and high SEO scores.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 border-default bg-offset p-8"
        style="min-height: 300px;"
      >
        <div
          class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-primary p-3 text-primary"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:search-web" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center font-extrabold text-2xl">
          Auditing of your social media presence
        </h1>
        <p>
          We understand that social media is a great way to reach your audience,
          without it you are missing out on a huge opportunity. We will audit
          your social media presence and provide you with a report on how you
          can improve.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 border-default bg-offset p-8"
        style="min-height: 300px;"
      >
        <div
          class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-primary p-3 text-primary"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:account" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center font-extrabold text-2xl">
          Constant support
        </h1>
        <p>
          Got a problem with your website? We will be there to help you out.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center sm:mx-32 md:mx-64"
    >
      <h1
        class="gradient-text text-center font-extrabold tracking-tight text-6xl"
      >
        Why we are different
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-center">
        We are more than just web developers, we are passionate about helping
        businesses grow. We also can develop custom-coded solutions to your
        problems, we are not limited by the constraints of a CMS and can develop
        anything you need. Whether thats a mobile app, a custom web app or a
        website.
      </p>
      <!-- <h1 class="mt-8 font-extrabold text-2xl">
        Interested in getting started with us?
      </h1>
      <a
        href="mailto:therunningbeta@gmail.com"
        class="mt-8 w-full rounded-md border border-black p-8 text-center font-bold text-primary transition duration-300 ease-in-out text-2xl hover:bg-black hover:text-white"
        role="button"
      >
        Email now
      </a> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
